OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrighton Marathon          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Forganisers apologise over  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcourse that was too long   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Brighton Marathon organisers have      
OL,6, apologised to runners after it emerged 
OL,7, the course was 568m (0.35 miles) too   
OL,8, long.                                  
OL,10,FAbout 12,000 participants set off from 
OL,11,FPreston Park from 09:45 BST on a course
OL,12,Fthey thought was 26.2 miles.           
OL,14,FOrganisers apologised for the error and
OL,15,Fsaid they hoped it had not "marred the 
OL,16,Fexperience" for runners.               
OL,18,FThey said the marathon was a "fantastic
OL,19,Fcomeback" after an 18-month hiatus due 
OL,20,Fto the coronavirus pandemic.           
